Yeah, I would agree with that.

00:56:55.630 --> 00:56:56.930
I think so much that what's
really frustrating a lot

00:56:56.930 --> 00:56:58.340
of times is that a narrative

00:56:58.340 --> 00:57:01.430
of the veterans are a sealed
society, and you sort of walk

00:57:01.430 --> 00:57:02.730
and operate within that.

00:57:02.730 --> 00:57:09.750
And that's frustrating that it
doesn't speak to the individual

00:57:09.750 --> 00:57:12.940
