thing, but you're not this.

00:57:24.270 --> 00:57:26.100
You're not going
to this experience

00:57:26.100 --> 00:57:28.740
that you had in your
life, right.

00:57:28.740 --> 00:57:32.710
You would like to be able to
take the veteran's mantle off

00:57:32.710 --> 00:57:35.010
at some point, you know,
like just be a person.

